{"tid":1687796,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馬國富商劉特佐被揭買巨鑽力追Miranda kerr","createTime":"2019-11-02T05:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T15:20:31.000Z","uid":173631,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6869cf0b7a01ad6d09ba41490bf42546eab074","tid":1687796,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:44:09.000Z","msg":"有無比個肥佬食快餐？？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6EhKaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6EhKaC.jpg&h=02fdf4d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHLkGXi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHLkGXi.jpg&h=54ad62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTz2aQD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTz2aQD.jpg&h=ea8ac09d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7TnaQD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7TnaQD.jpg&h=c3bbbe13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ei5T1Xj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEi5T1Xj.jpg&h=52bfa45b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xibgfhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXibgfhj.jpg&h=0f652b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170616/photo/bkn-20170616153934382-0616_00862_001_01p.jpg?20170617212529\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170616%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170616153934382-0616_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20170617212529&h=1a353c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬來西亞富商劉特佐(Jho Low)去年被揭發涉及一宗嚴重案件，當時連奧斯卡影帝&ldquo;裏奧仔&rdquo;裏奧勒度狄卡比奧（Leonardo DiCaprio）亦牽涉在內，前日再爆出劉特佐於三年前曾以贓款買下鉆石力追澳洲索模Miranda Kerr!<br />\n<br />\n據《紐約郵報》(New York Post)引述司法部的報告指，現年35歲的劉特佐屢次利用1MDB的基金買厚禮追求Miranda!其中2014年的情人節他就以129萬美元(約1,006萬港元)買下11.72卡心型鉆石送給當時已與影星奧蘭度布林(Orlando Bloom)離婚的Miranda，作為情人節禮物!據報告指劉特佐當時向紐約著名珠寶設計師Lorraine Schwartz訂購心形鉆石，並註明他的budget為100萬至200萬美元(約780萬至1,600萬港元)，最終埋單要129萬美元。同年11月，劉特佐再幫襯同一店鋪花380萬美元（約2,964萬港元）買下8.88卡鉆石墜及以198萬美元（約1,544萬港元）買了11卡鉆石耳環、項鏈、戒指等，來再次送禮給Miranda!最後成功打動Miranda，二人拍拖一年，2015年Miranda就與Snapchat創辦人Evan Spiegel拍拖，上月底二人在洛杉磯寓所低調結婚。<br />\n<br />\n由於劉特佐涉以贓款來買禮物贈Miranda，現司法部門好大機會要求Miranda歸還那些巨額禮物，據知Miranda得知事件之後一直合作全力協助司法部調查，目前Miranda仍擁有那些&ldquo;禮物&rdquo;，而有關部門尚未要求Miranda歸還。"},{"pid":"dbbd4477bcf2a947cf771ffff15a2b648e8a0ae5","tid":1687796,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e6013808fdb7b7bcd1db657428e7aad87dc59f","tid":1687796,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"拍拖一年 點會唔扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10851b585650248f33643e09a9eb10b275dfed87","tid":1687796,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"屌原來都係雞"},{"pid":"84fc5764c73ce83b264f1e60ce3dcde6e4e474e0","tid":1687796,"uid":105693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:57:41.000Z","msg":"拍拖一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce69d1cb6c456048bd5b45d165f27724ef90980","tid":1687796,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T06:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57148d601b55436c65c1a9e9d019eab448d0411","tid":1687796,"uid":74435,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:15:47.000Z","msg":"一路都有人話呢條女好勢利"},{"pid":"355e35660fb6877a36a11e23f15e69bc15863b31","tid":1687796,"uid"